<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>CatchCatch | 결제 상세내역</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/payment-detail.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="popup-wrap">
    <div class="popup-card">

        <header class="popup-header">
            <div class="small">CatchCatch Payment Detail</div>
            <h1>결제 상세내역</h1>
            <p>결제번호, 예매번호, 공연 정보와 결제 상태를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
        </header>

        <!-- 결제 정보 -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>결제 정보</h2>

            <table class="detail-table">
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <th>결제번호</th>
                    <td>{{payment.paymentId}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>PG 거래번호</th>
                    <td>{{payment.pgTxIdText}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>예매번호</th>
                    <td>{{payment.bookingNumber}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>결제수단</th>
                    <td>{{payment.method}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>결제상태</th>
                    <td>{{payment.statusLabel}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>결제요청일</th>
                    <td>{{payment.createdAtText}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>결제완료일</th>
                    <td>{{payment.paidAtText}}</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <!-- 예매 정보 -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>예매 정보</h2>

            <table class="detail-table">
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <th>공연명</th>
                    <td>{{payment.concertTitle}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>공연날짜</th>
                    <td>{{payment.sessionDateText}}</td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <th>좌석</th>
                    <td>{{payment.seatText}}</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <!-- 금액 정보 -->
        <section class="price-box">
            <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price-label">최종 결제 금액</span>
                <span class="price-value">{{payment.amountText}}</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="notice">
            결제 취소 및 환불은 공연일, 예매 상태, 취소 시점에 따라 제한될 수 있습니다.
            자세한 내용은 취소/환불 안내를 확인해주세요.
        </div>

        <div class="button-area">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline" onclick="window.print()">인쇄</button>

            {{#payment.canRefund}}
                <button type="button"
                        class="btn btn-danger"
                        onclick="location.href='/refunds/new?paymentId={{payment.id}}'">
                환불 신청
                </button>
            {{/payment.canRefund}}

            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.close()">닫기</button>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>